               <p>SECOND COUNT, the same, only stating it to be the property of some person unknown.</p>
               <p>JOHN BURR. I am a <rs id="t18180114-179-deflabel966" type="occupation">labourer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-179-defend1237 t18180114-179-deflabel966"></join> in the East India Company's service, and so was the prisoner. On the 9th of January he was employed at <placeName id="t18180114-179-crimeloc967">Blackwall</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18180114-179-crimeloc967" type="placeName" value="Blackwall"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18180114-179-crimeloc967" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-179-off963 t18180114-179-crimeloc967"></join> in sending away pepper from the pile. I saw him take some, and put it in his breeches, and went for Mr. Brown.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180114-179-person1239">
                  WILLIAM 
                  BROWN
               <interp inst="t18180114-179-person1239" type="surname" value="BROWN"></interp>
