                     <interp inst="t18180114-179-person1239" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an elder in the Company's service. I took the prisoner into a private room, and found 2lbs. of pepper in his breeches, in a bag.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I have been twelve years in the service.</p>
